# ============================================================
# Security Notes
# ============================================================
# 1. Keep INCOLLABE_API_KEY secret (like a password)
# 2. Never commit it to Git (add .env to .gitignore)
# 3. Never expose it in client-side code
# 4. Only use it in your backend server
# 5. If compromised, contact Incollabe team immediately
